    • Constructor Detail

      • AppState

        private AppState()
        The AppState Constructor is private so instances of the AppState Class cannot be created using the new keyword. When the singleton AppState object is created the toDoLists field is instantiated with an ArrayList of ToDoLists and selectedList is set to null. EditPressed is a boolean value by default set to false.
